<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>CC Daily Brief — Friday, April 17, 2026</title>
<style>
  @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=DM+Sans:ital,opsz,wght@0,9..40,300;0,9..40,500;0,9..40,700;1,9..40,400&family=Playfair+Display:wght@700;900&display=swap');

  :root {
    --bg: #0e0e11;
    --surface: #17171c;
    --surface-raised: #1e1e25;
    --border: #2a2a35;
    --text: #e8e6e3;
    --text-muted: #8a8a96;
    --accent: #c9a45c;
    --accent-glow: rgba(201,164,92,0.15);
    --critical: #ef4444;
    --critical-bg: rgba(239,68,68,0.1);
    --urgent: #f97316;
    --urgent-bg: rgba(249,115,22,0.1);
    --high: #eab308;
    --high-bg: rgba(234,179,8,0.08);
    --warning: #f59e0b;
    --warning-bg: rgba(245,158,11,0.08);
    --medium: #3b82f6;
    --medium-bg: rgba(59,130,246,0.08);
    --done: #22c55e;
    --done-bg: rgba(34,197,94,0.08);
    --green: #22c55e;
    --graphite: #6b7280;
    --lavender: #a78bfa;
    --blue: #3b82f6;
  }

  * { margin:0; padding:0; box-sizing:border-box; }

  body {
    background: var(--bg);
    color: var(--text);
    font-family: 'DM Sans', system-ui, sans-serif;
    line-height: 1.6;
    min-height: 100vh;
  }

  .noise {
    position: fixed; inset:0; z-index:0; pointer-events:none; opacity:0.03;
    background-image: url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg viewBox='0 0 256 256' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cfilter id='n'%3E%3CfeTurbulence type='fractalNoise' baseFrequency='0.9' numOctaves='4' stitchTiles='stitch'/%3E%3C/filter%3E%3Crect width='100%25' height='100%25' filter='url(%23n)'/%3E%3C/svg%3E");
  }

  .container {
    position: relative; z-index:1;
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 2rem 1.5rem 4rem;
  }

  /* HEADER */
  .header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    padding-bottom: 1.5rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .header-brand {
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .header h1 {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', Georgia, serif;
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 900;
    color: var(--text);
    line-height: 1.15;
    margin-bottom: 0.2rem;
  }

  .header-date {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
  }

  .header-meta {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  /* COUNTDOWN BANNER */
  .countdown-banner {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(239,68,68,0.15) 0%, rgba(249,115,22,0.1) 100%);
    border: 1px solid rgba(239,68,68,0.3);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .countdown-label {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .countdown-text {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', Georgia, serif;
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 900;
    color: var(--critical);
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }

  .countdown-days {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  /* SECTION */
  .section {
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  .section-title {
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.6rem;
    user-select: none;
  }

  .section-title::after {
    content: '';
    flex: 1;
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--border);
  }

  .section-count {
    background: var(--surface-raised);
    color: var(--text-muted);
    padding: 0.1rem 0.5rem;
    border-radius: 100px;
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .section-content {
    width: 100%;
    overflow: visible;
  }

  /* CARDS */
  .card {
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
    transition: border-color 0.2s;
  }

  .card:hover {
    border-color: var(--accent);
  }

  .card.urgent-card {
    border-left: 3px solid var(--urgent);
  }

  .card.critical-card {
    border-left: 3px solid var(--critical);
  }

  .card.success-card {
    border-left: 3px solid var(--green);
  }

  .card.warning-card {
    border-left: 3px solid var(--warning);
  }

  .card-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
  }

  .card-title {
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 0.92rem;
    color: var(--text);
    line-height: 1.35;
    flex: 1;
  }

  .card-meta {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.4rem;
    align-items: center;
    margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
  }

  .badge {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 0.15rem 0.55rem;
    border-radius: 100px;
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.03em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  .badge-critical { background: var(--critical-bg); color: var(--critical); border: 1px solid rgba(239,68,68,0.3); }
  .badge-urgent { background: var(--urgent-bg); color: var(--urgent); border: 1px solid rgba(249,115,22,0.3); }
  .badge-high { background: var(--high-bg); color: var(--high); border: 1px solid rgba(234,179,8,0.2); }
  .badge-warning { background: var(--warning-bg); color: var(--warning); border: 1px solid rgba(245,158,11,0.2); }
  .badge-medium { background: var(--medium-bg); color: var(--medium); border: 1px solid rgba(59,130,246,0.2); }
  .badge-done { background: var(--done-bg); color: var(--done); border: 1px solid rgba(34,197,94,0.3); }
  .badge-revenue { background: var(--done-bg); color: var(--done); border: 1px solid rgba(34,197,94,0.3); }
  .badge-client { background: var(--accent-glow); color: var(--accent); border: 1px solid rgba(201,164,92,0.25); }
  .badge-category { background: var(--surface-raised); color: var(--text-muted); border: 1px solid var(--border); }

  .card-note {
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .card-action {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
    padding-top: 0.5rem;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(201,164,92,0.1);
  }

  /* TIMELINE */
  .timeline {
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
  }

  .timeline-item {
    position: relative;
    margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
  }

  .timeline-item::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: -1.75rem;
    top: 1.2rem;
    width: 10px;
    height: 10px;
    background: var(--accent);
    border: 2px solid var(--bg);
    border-radius: 50%;
  }

  .timeline-time {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-bottom: 0.2rem;
  }

  .timeline-event {
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 0.2rem;
  }

  .timeline-note {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  /* HEALTH CARDS */
  .health-card {
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
  }

  .health-card.critical {
    border-left: 3px solid var(--critical);
    background: rgba(239,68,68,0.05);
  }

  .health-card.warning {
    border-left: 3px solid var(--warning);
  }

  .health-card.healthy {
    border-left: 3px solid var(--green);
  }

  .health-title {
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 0.92rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
  }

  .health-meta {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.4rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  .health-note {
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .health-indicator {
    display: inline-block;
    width: 12px;
    height: 12px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    margin-right: 0.4rem;
    vertical-align: middle;
  }

  .health-indicator.healthy { background: var(--green); }
  .health-indicator.warning { background: var(--warning); }
  .health-indicator.critical { background: var(--critical); }

  /* CHECKBOX CARDS */
  .checkbox-card {
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 0.75rem;
  }

  .checkbox-input {
    width: 18px;
    height: 18px;
    min-width: 18px;
    border: 2px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 4px;
    background: var(--surface-raised);
    cursor: pointer;
    margin-top: 0.15rem;
    appearance: none;
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }

  .checkbox-input:hover {
    border-color: var(--accent);
  }

  .checkbox-input:checked {
    background: var(--accent);
    border-color: var(--accent);
  }

  .checkbox-content {
    flex: 1;
  }

  .checkbox-title {
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 0.92rem;
    color: var(--text);
    margin-bottom: 0.2rem;
  }

  .checkbox-meta {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.4rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.2rem;
  }

  .checkbox-note {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  /* CASH FLOW */
  .cash-flow-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
    gap: 0.8rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .cash-item {
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 1rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .cash-label {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
  }

  .cash-value {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', Georgia, serif;
    font-size: 1.6rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  .cash-flow-breakdown {
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
  }

  .breakdown-item {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 0.5rem 0;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .breakdown-item:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  .breakdown-client {
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text);
  }

  .breakdown-amount {
    color: var(--accent);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .breakdown-status {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  .breakdown-status.warning {
    color: var(--warning);
  }

  .breakdown-status.healthy {
    color: var(--green);
  }

  /* COMPETITOR CARDS */
  .competitor-card {
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .competitor-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: start;
    justify-content: space-between;
    margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
  }

  .competitor-name {
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--text);
  }

  .competitor-threat {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.4rem;
  }

  .threat-badge {
    padding: 0.15rem 0.55rem;
    border-radius: 100px;
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .threat-high {
    background: var(--critical-bg);
    color: var(--critical);
    border: 1px solid rgba(239,68,68,0.3);
  }

  .threat-medium {
    background: var(--warning-bg);
    color: var(--warning);
    border: 1px solid rgba(245,158,11,0.2);
  }

  .threat-low {
    background: var(--medium-bg);
    color: var(--medium);
    border: 1px solid rgba(59,130,246,0.2);
  }

  .threat-very-high {
    background: var(--critical-bg);
    color: var(--critical);
    border: 1px solid rgba(239,68,68,0.3);
  }

  .competitor-metrics {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(80px, 1fr));
    gap: 0.8rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
  }

  .metric {
    background: var(--surface-raised);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 0.6rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .metric-label {
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 0.2rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .metric-value {
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  .competitor-details {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
  }

  .competitor-opportunity {
    background: rgba(34,197,94,0.05);
    border-left: 3px solid var(--green);
    padding: 0.75rem;
    border-radius: 6px;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
  }

  /* GOALS PROGRESS */
  .goal-card {
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
  }

  .goal-title {
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 0.92rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
  }

  .goal-meta {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
  }

  .progress-bar {
    background: var(--surface-raised);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 4px;
    height: 6px;
    overflow: hidden;
    margin: 0.4rem 0;
  }

  .progress-fill {
    height: 100%;
    background: var(--accent);
    transition: width 0.3s;
  }

  /* SEO HEALTH BADGES */
  .seo-score {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .seo-score.excellent { background: rgba(34,197,94,0.15); color: var(--green); border: 1px solid rgba(34,197,94,0.3); }
  .seo-score.good { background: rgba(59,130,246,0.15); color: var(--blue); border: 1px solid rgba(59,130,246,0.3); }
  .seo-score.warning { background: var(--warning-bg); color: var(--warning); border: 1px solid rgba(245,158,11,0.3); }
  .seo-score.poor { background: var(--critical-bg); color: var(--critical); border: 1px solid rgba(239,68,68,0.3); }

  .seo-card {
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
  }

  .seo-site {
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 0.92rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
  }

  .seo-details {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  /* MARKET INSIGHTS */
  .insight-card {
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
  }

  .insight-source {
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .insight-title {
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    color: var(--text);
    margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  .insight-note {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  /* LAYOUT ADJUSTMENTS */
  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .container {
      padding: 1.5rem 1rem 3rem;
    }

    .header h1 {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
    }

    .countdown-text {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .card {
      padding: 0.85rem 1rem;
    }

    .card-title {
      font-size: 0.88rem;
    }

    .section-title {
      font-size: 0.65rem;
    }
  }

</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="noise"></div>

<div class="container">

  <!-- HEADER -->
  <div class="header">
    <div class="header-brand">Constant Creates</div>
    <h1>Daily Brief</h1>
    <div class="header-date">Friday, April 17, 2026</div>
    <div class="header-meta">Peleta meeting 1 PM · Friday CEO check-in · VMC header videos due today</div>
  </div>

  <!-- COUNTDOWN BANNER -->
  <div class="countdown-banner">
    <div class="countdown-label">Featured Goal</div>
    <div class="countdown-text">45 Days</div>
    <div class="countdown-days">Quit Rooks by June 1, 2026</div>
  </div>

  <!-- 1. URGENT ACTIONS -->
  <div class="section">
    <div class="section-title">
      Urgent Actions
      <div class="section-count">3</div>
    </div>
    <div class="section-content">
      <div class="card critical-card">
        <div class="card-header">
          <div>
            <div class="card-title">Peleta Henderson — Jus' Poetic meeting at 1 PM TODAY</div>
            <div class="card-meta">
              <span class="badge badge-revenue">REVENUE</span>
              <span class="badge badge-high">HOT PROSPECT</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card-note"><strong>Why:</strong> Meeting scheduled for 1 PM to discuss the $300/mo blog &amp; SEO retainer pitch. Peleta already left a 5-star Google review Mar 24 — she's warm and ready. This is the strongest near-term win for closing the gap to $6K.</div>
        <div class="card-action"><strong>Action:</strong> Review the pitch deck, have pricing ($300/mo base, $500/mo premium) and deliverables clear. Lead with the Google review momentum — her words sell this better than yours.</div>
      </div>

      <div class="card warning-card">
        <div class="card-header">
          <div>
            <div class="card-title">Hallwood Q1 Invoice — $925, 9 days overdue</div>
            <div class="card-meta">
              <span class="badge badge-revenue">REVENUE</span>
              <span class="badge badge-warning">FOLLOW-UP</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card-note"><strong>Why:</strong> Due Apr 8, today is Apr 17. Clay confirmed Apr 13 he never saw the original and asked you to resend — you did. He replied Apr 14 about LinkedIn Premium but did NOT address the invoice. Friendly nudge is warranted before the weekend.</div>
        <div class="card-action"><strong>Action:</strong> Send a short, warm follow-up reply to Clay's Apr 14 LinkedIn email — reference the invoice casually ("just wanted to double-check the Q1 invoice reached you this time — happy to resend the ACH details"). Keep the LinkedIn Premium work moving as the headline.</div>
      </div>

      <div class="card warning-card">
        <div class="card-header">
          <div>
            <div class="card-title">Derek Mardones — 6 days silent, 7-day threshold tomorrow</div>
            <div class="card-meta">
              <span class="badge badge-urgent">URGENCY</span>
              <span class="badge badge-done">ACTIVE CLIENT</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card-note"><strong>Why:</strong> Email sent Apr 11 ("Photo Shoot Reschedule + Behind the Brand") — Derek hasn't replied in 6 days. Derek prefers texting, so the silence likely means the email got buried, not a problem. Text nudge today keeps the photo shoot on track for next week.</div>
        <div class="card-action"><strong>Action:</strong> Send a short, warm iMessage: "Hey Derek! Trying to lock in a reschedule for the photo shoot — any chance Mon/Fri AM or weekend works for you? Also got a fun idea to run past you when you have a sec. 🐝"</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- 2. TODAY'S SCHEDULE -->
  <div class="section">
    <div class="section-title">
      Today's Schedule (Friday)
      <div class="section-count">6</div>
    </div>
    <div class="section-content">
      <div class="timeline">
        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-time">8:00 AM - 9:30 AM</div>
          <div class="timeline-event">Morning block — email triage + Peleta pitch prep</div>
          <div class="timeline-note">Review morning briefing, send stale drafts (Kim, Lydia, Sasha), finalize Peleta pitch talking points</div>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-time">10:30 AM - 12:00 PM</div>
